{"tid":1967570,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"伯克希爾哈撒韋今年在股票中已經虧損465億美元","createTime":"2020-04-11T04:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T11:02:08.000Z","uid":82340,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"11c0ff3128e3e0d278295ad07a0aa349bab9bad0","tid":1967570,"uid":82340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:45:46.000Z","msg":"伯克希爾哈撒韋今年在股票中已經虧損465億美元<br />\n<br />\n  來源：證券時報<br />\n<br />\n  據證券時報報道，統計顯示，截至今日，今年以來，巴菲特的伯克希爾哈撒韋公司在股票中已經損失465億美元，換算成人民幣3255億元（相當於A股格力電器或萬科A的市值），佔其股票持倉的19%。具體個股看，伯克希爾哈撒韋公司持倉中美國銀行、富國銀行、蘋果公司、美國運通、美國合衆銀行、達美航空、可口可樂、摩根大通、聯合航空、卡夫亨氏、紐約梅隆銀行的虧損額均超10億美元，在其最大持倉蘋果公司上，虧損60多億美元。"},{"pid":"a4c4c04e85640996e607153b77b9fa5e7f33a1a5","tid":1967570,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:48:16.000Z","msg":"有命先算啦"},{"pid":"4c1459d7feea0906242e75e5addd31d678f62324","tid":1967570,"uid":135867,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"你不會投資？"},{"pid":"9a1fa455824c499b06ecc0414b61f37efa1a6d09","tid":1967570,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"點譯個音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf2c78c7bdf6e753e61ddc2f6c034d6e5439f42","tid":1967570,"uid":26708,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"4c1459d7feea0906242e75e5addd31d678f62324","tid":1967570,"uid":135867,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"你不會投資？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:56:29.000Z","msg":"讓巴菲特幫你投資吧"},{"pid":"c868be0649c25676b4ce68e9e1e9215bf9c20f31","tid":1967570,"uid":254551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:56:50.000Z","msg":"肯定無用etoro"},{"pid":"03b327b9a72fa82a433abd854e8ddc8bca380de5","tid":1967570,"uid":205462,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:57:05.000Z","msg":"Berkshire Hathaway, 直接打英文好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/